<view class="container">
    <view class="detail-header">
        <view class="header-title">
            <view class="title-content">
                抖音直播充场
            </view>
            <view class="title-price">
                30元/小时
            </view>
        </view>
        <view class="header-tag">
            <view class="block">
                <t-tag class="block-tag" theme="primary">日结</t-tag>
                <t-tag class="block-tag" theme="primary">男女不限</t-tag>
            </view>
        </view>
        <view class="header-update">
            <view class="update-browsing">
                <view class="browsing-icon">
                    <t-icon name="browse" size="48rpx" data-name="browse"/>
                </view>
                <view class="browsing-text">
                    <span>677</span>人浏览
                </view>
                <view class="browsing-time">
                    更新时间:<span>2022-12-08 14:12:56</span>
                </view>
            </view>
        </view>
    </view>
    <view class="detail-address">
        <view class="address-item">
            <view class="item-line"></view>
            <view class="item-name">工作地点</view>
            <view class="item-small">(点击可一键复制)</view>
        </view>
        <view class="address-detail">
            大鹏新区啊
        </view>
    </view>
    <view class="detail-address">
        <view class="address-item">
            <view class="item-line"></view>
            <view class="item-name">工作详情</view>
        </view>
        <view class="address-detail">  
            <text class="detail-text">
            工作内容
                将商家指定的信息复制粘贴到朋友圈即可，操作简单，两分钟即可
                工作过要求 
                1、下午13:00到晚上2：00时间自由
                2、通过位置测试才能做任务微信近期没有被封号过
                3、不限时间和地点
                薪资待遇
                10-50/h(每天可做)
                一小时一结
            </text>
        </view>
    </view>
    <view class="detail-source">
        <view class="source-icon">
            <t-icon name="internet" size="48rpx" data-name="internet"/>
        </view>
        <view class="source-text">
            <span class="text-title">信息来源</span><span class="text-value">：商家发布</span>
        </view>
    </view>
    <view class="detail-notify">
        <view class="detail-notifys">
            <view class="notify-icon">
            <t-icon name="notification" size="48rpx" data-name="notification"/>
            </view>
            <view class="notify-text">
                <span class="text-title">
                龙猫兼职提醒您：在招聘，录用期间以任何理由索要财务，扣押证件，均属违法行为，请您提高警惕
                </span>
            </view>
        </view>
       <view class="detail-tis">添加商家联系信息未通过可能是商家正忙或人员已招满！</view>
    </view>
    <view class="detail-footer">
        <t-button  theme="primary" block size="large" bind:tap="showDialog">获取联系方式</t-button>
    </view>
    <t-dialog
    visible="{{showWithInput}}"
    title="带输入框对话框"
    confirm-btn='确认按钮'
    bind:confirm="closeDialog"
  >
    <view slot="content" class="dialog-content">
        <view class="content-image">
            <view class="image-icon">
                <t-icon name="logo-qq" size="48rpx" data-name="logo-qq" bind:click="onIconTap" />
            </view>
            <view class="image-title">
                <view>QQ联系方式 </view>
            </view>
            <view class="image-btn">
                <t-button variant="outline" theme="primary" size="small">点击复制</t-button>
            </view>
        </view>

        <view class="content-image">
            <view class="image-icon">
                <t-icon name="logo-wechat" size="48rpx" data-name="logo-wechat" bind:click="onIconTap" />
            </view>
            <view class="image-title">
                <view>微信联系方式 </view>
            </view>
            <view class="image-btn">
                <t-button variant="outline" theme="primary" size="small">点击复制</t-button>
            </view>
        </view>

        <view class="content-image">
            <view class="image-icon">
                <t-icon name="service" size="48rpx" data-name="service" bind:click="onIconTap" />
            </view>
            <view class="image-title">
                <view>其他联系方式 </view>
            </view>
            <view class="image-btn">
                <t-button variant="outline" theme="primary" size="small">点击复制</t-button>
            </view>
        </view>

        <view class="content-image">
            <view class="image-icon">
                <t-icon name="image" size="48rpx" data-name="image" bind:click="onIconTap" />
            </view>
            <view class="image-title">
                <view>图片联系方式 </view>
            </view>
            <view class="image-btn">
                <t-button variant="outline" theme="primary" size="small">点击查看</t-button>
            </view>
        </view>

    </view>
  </t-dialog> 
</view>